title: Making post so my level syncs with the boards
body: Seems silly that I have to do this but there it is.

replies.body: I see your profile has synced now.  If you are still unable to post, your local files may need to be cleaned up by [clearing your cache and cookies](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies).  Please let me know if you're still experiencing any issues.
It's all good now. Thanks for the concern and comment though. Glad to know there are still reds out there.
And yet after posting this it still wont let me create a discussion anywhere other than H and S
